players.name: Nafian Alionzi
players.summary: Legasson Nafian Alionzi Alionzi is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Ethiopian Premier League club Defence Force and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Denis Onyango
players.summary: Denis Masinde Onyango is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for South African Premier Soccer League club Mamelodi Sundowns and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Salim Magoola
players.summary: Omar Jamal Salim Magoola, commonly known as Jamal Salim, is a Ugandan footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Richards Bay.

players.name: Timothy Awany
players.summary: Timothy Dennis Awany is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a defender for Israeli Premier League club Ashdod and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Toby Sibbick
players.summary: Toby Peter Sibbick is a professional footballer who plays as a centre-back or right-back for EFL League One club Burton Albion. Born in England, he plays for the Uganda national football team.

players.name: Elio Capradossi
players.summary: Elio Capradossi is a professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Liga I club Universitatea Cluj. A former youth international for Italy, he plays for the Uganda national team.

players.name: Jordan Obita
players.summary: Jordan John Obita is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as left-back or winger for Scottish Premiership club Hibernian, and the Uganda national football team.

players.name: Isaac Muleme
players.summary: Isaac Muleme is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a left-back.

players.name: Aziz Kayondo
players.summary: Aziz Abdu Kayondo is a Ugandan footballer who plays as a defender for Czech club Slovan Liberec and the Uganda national football team.

players.name: Hilary Mukundane
players.summary: Hilary Panuel Mukundane is a Ugandan footballer who plays as a centre-back for Vipers SC and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Kenneth Semakula
players.summary: Kenneth Semakula is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as defender for Saudi club Al-Adalah and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Bobosi Byaruhanga
players.summary: Bobosi Byaruhanga is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for USL Championship club Oakland Roots and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Khalid Aucho
players.summary: Khalid Aucho is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder for Tanzanian Premier League club Singida Black Stars and captains the Uganda national team.

players.name: Travis Mutyaba
players.summary: Travis Mutyaba is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays for Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1 club CS Sfaxien and formerly played for French Championnat National 2 club Bordeaux and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Baba Alhassan
players.summary: Baba Alhassan is a professional footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder or a centre-back for Liga I club FCSB. Born in Ghana, he represents Uganda at international level.

players.name: Ronald Ssekiganda
players.summary: Ronald Ssekiganda is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Rwanda Premier League club APR and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Allan Okello
players.summary: Allan Okello is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays for Vipers SC and the Uganda national team as an attacking midfielder.

players.name: Rogers Mato
players.summary: Rogers Mato Kassim is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays for Macedonian First Football League club Vardar and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Uche Ikpeazu
players.summary: Karl Anthony Uchechukwu Mubiru Ikpeazu is a professional footballer who plays as a forward for Scottish Championship club St Johnstone. Born in England, he plays for the Uganda national team.

players.name: Steven Mukwala
players.summary: Steven Mukwala is a Ugandan professional footballer who currently plays as a striker for NBC premier league club Simba Sc, before joining them he was Asante Kotoko Sc player. He played Vipers SC and loaned at Maroons FC of Uganda Premier League.

players.name: Denis Omedi
players.summary: Denis Omedi is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a striker for Rwanda Premier League club APR and the Uganda national football team.

players.name: Reagan Mpande
players.summary: Reagan Mpande is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a forward for the Uganda Premier League club SC Villa.

players.name: Jude Ssemugabi
players.summary: Jude Ssemugabi is a Ugandan professional footballer who also plays as forward for Jamus in the South Sudan Premier League and the Uganda national football team.

players.name: Shafik Nana Kwikiriza
players.summary: Shafik Nana Kwikiriza is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a forward for KCCA FC in the Uganda Premier League and the Uganda national team.

players.name: Melvyn Lorenzen
players.summary: Melvyn Lorenzen is a professional footballer who plays as a forward or a winger for Thai League 1 club Muangthong United. Born in England with German nationality, he has represented the Uganda national team.

players.name: Ivan Ahimbisibwe
players.summary: Ivan Ahimbisibwe is a Ugandan professional footballer who plays as a forward for KCCA FC in the Uganda Premier League and the Uganda national football team.
